manifest.name: @sentry/utils
manifest.description: Utilities for all Sentry JavaScript SDKs
manifest.readme: # Sentry JavaScript SDK Utilities [![npm version](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/@sentry/utils.svg)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@sentry/utils) [![npm dm](https://img.shields.io/npm/dm/@sentry/utils.svg)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@sentry/utils) [![npm dt](https://img.shields.io/npm/dt/@sentry/utils.svg)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@sentry/utils) ## Links - [Official SDK Docs](https://docs.sentry.io/quickstart/) - [TypeDoc](http://getsentry.github.io/sentry-javascript/) ## General Common utilities used by the Sentry JavaScript SDKs. Note: This package is only meant to be used internally, and as such is not part of our public API contract and does not follow semver.
